OL,17,Fof rain pushes east Friday with
OL,18,Fshowers following later. Showers or
OL,19,Flonger spells of rain on Saturday.
OL,20,FOccasionally windy. Mostly dry, bright
OL,21,FSunday, chance of the odd shower.
